OL,7,FMs Docx, told us: "We would always
OL,8,Fencourage staff to come forward with
OL,9,Fany concerns and believe it is
OL,10,Fparamount that people feel comfortable
OL,11,Fin doing so. Our priority is to ensure
OL,12,Fthese issues are identified, properly
OL,13,Finvestigated and dealt with fairly."
